-2 & 1 \\ 
3 & -4 \end{array}
\right)\left( \begin{array}{rr}
x & 2 \\ 
1 & y \end{array}
\right)=\left( \begin{array}{rr}
-3 & 1 \\ 
2 & -14 \end{array}
\right)$.

